{
  "stem": "22750.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, whatever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, it was a lot of folks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I tell you only what I know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know I don't know everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because at that time, a lot of them from the area spread all over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--were you were afraid, also, of Ukrainians?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, for any live human, doesn't matter who.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Any human alive, we are afraid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not afraid for animals or for something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only because the population became animals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is not a make-up story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what the story is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's what it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe I'm not describing everything, every details.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because it was more-- even the details was more certain things-- was more scary and wondering, how could this happen?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Was-- because in a normal time, this is not happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the normal time made the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The help, from our area, Ukrainian business and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Czechs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was other ones.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Ukraine, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they were poor in their mentality.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because we was-- the whole areas was not educated like over in the United States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody went to school as a child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if you haven't got education, your feeling is different, like an animal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the reason, this was my reason, to make him scared, and scared out of their mind to kill us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I didn't-- you couldn't exam their nature.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they are good nature or bad nature, I accept only my mind, what my mind dictate me that time, to give him in case he will kill me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe because I will-- I will tell you a story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's not-- some people, why they survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they also paid up, certain people, certain things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not pay.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not talking money about pays, They paid with their lives too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
